'''貝登堡墓'''（{{lang-en|Baden-Powell Grave}}）是[[羅伯特·貝登堡|羅伯特·貝登堡]]與其妻子[[奧莉芙·貝登堡|奧莉芙·貝登堡]]的墓地，位於[[肯亞|肯亞]]的[[尼耶利|尼耶利]]，靠近[[肯亞山|肯亞山]]。貝登堡爵士於1941年過世，並葬於{{link-en|馬賽自然公園|Wajee Nature Park}}的聖彼得墓園（{{lang|en|St. Peter's Cemetery}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://scout.org/bp |title=Baden-Powell |publisher=Scout.org |date=8 January 1941 |accessdate=4 March 2014 |archive-date=2021-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402093756/https://www.scout.org/bp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的墓碑刻上了一個大圓，圓心點上一個黑點，在追蹤記號中代表「我已回」<ref>{{Find a Grave|1271|Robert Stephenson Smyth Baden-Powell|accessdate=24 October 2010}}</ref>。當貝登堡夫人過世時，她的骨灰被送到肯亞，並葬在貝登堡的旁邊。肯亞宣布貝登堡墓為國家名勝古蹟<ref name="dualgrave">{{Find a Grave|1272|Olave St. Clair Baden-Powell|accessdate=24 October 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.businessdailyafrica.com/-/539444/651866/-/view/printVersion/-/4w09bwz/-/index.html |title=The burden of Lord Baden Powell's resting place – Home |publisher=businessdailyafrica.com |date= |accessdate=4 March 2014 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924163659/https://www.businessdailyafrica.com/-/539444/651866/-/view/printVersion/-/4w09bwz/-/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

